Package hackcompiler

package hackcompiler
  • Class
    Description
    Assembler
    Assembler will serve as the central class that will call all other methods as needed.
    Code
    Translates Hack assembly language mnemonics into binary code.
    Compare
    A class containing helpful constants and one method in order to check yourFile.hack against yourFileCompare.hack and print out a pretty table.
    Parser
    Parser: The main function of the parser is to break each assembly command into its underlying components (fields and symbols).
    Parser.Instruction
    This enum will be used to identify the type of the current instruction.
    SymbolTable
    SymbolTable: Keeps a correspondence between symbolic labels and numeric addresses.
